{"article_id":"V67l5oI8QijhhaCg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The family of a US student","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"who died","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"after he was jailed in North Korea","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"have implicitly rebuked President Donald Trump 's lauding of Kim Jong-un .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Otto Warmbier 's parents said","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"they had been `` respectful '' during Mr Trump and the North Korean leader 's recent summit ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"but were now speaking out .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"They said","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"`` no excuse or lavish praise can change ''","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"that `` Kim and his evil regime '' killed their son .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Their statement came","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"after Mr Trump heaped compliments on Mr Kim .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Mr Trump 's second nuclear summit with Mr Kim this week in Vietnam ended without agreement .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"After the family 's blistering statement was released ,","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"Mr Trump took to Twitter","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"where he said","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"he had been `` misinterpreted '' .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The family released a brief statement on Friday","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"condemning praise for the North Korean leader ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"without mentioning Mr Trump by name .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"`` We have been respectful during this summit process .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Now we must speak out , ''","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"wrote Fred and Cindy Warmbier .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"`` Kim and his evil regime are responsible for the death of our son Otto . `` Kim and his evil regime are responsible for unimaginable cruelty and inhumanity .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"Warmbier was jailed in Pyongyang in January 2016 during an organised tour ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"accused of stealing a hotel poster .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"The University of Virginia student was sentenced to 15 years ' hard labour ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"but released after 17 months .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"The 22-year-old was returned to the US in a vegetative state in June 2017 ,","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"and died days later in his hometown of Cincinnati , Ohio .","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"The Warmbiers attended the 2018 State of the Union speech as the president 's guests ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"weeping","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"as he called them `` powerful witnesses to a menace","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that threatens our world '' .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Mr Trump told reporters in Hanoi on Thursday morning ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"referring to Mr Warmbier 's death :","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"`` He","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"[ Mr Kim ]","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"tells me","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"he did n't know about it ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"and I will take him at his word . ''","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"The president added","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that the North Korean leader felt `` very badly '' about the case .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"In a Fox News interview","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"aired late on Thursday ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Mr Trump said","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Mr Kim was `` sharp","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"as you can be ''","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"and `` a real leader '' .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"`` Some people say","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"I should n't like him , ''","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"the US president told host Sean Hannity , a vocal Trump advocate .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"`` Why should n't I like him ? ''","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"The president","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"-","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"who is now back at the White House -","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"he gets along `` really well '' with Mr Kim .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"`` And he 's a real personality","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and he 's very smart .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"He 's sharp","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"as you can be ,","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"and he 's a real leader ,","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"and he 's pretty mercurial .","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"`` I do n't say that necessarily in a bad way ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"but he 's a pretty mercurial guy . ''","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"Explaining why the summit broke down ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Mr Trump said :","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"`` Well , they wanted to denuke certain areas","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"and I wanted everything . ''","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"The Fox host defended the president 's decision","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"to walk away ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"recommending a reading of Mr Trump 's book , The Art of the Deal ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"to truly `` understand '' his tactics .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"After the talks broke down ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"North Korean officials contradicted Mr Trump 's contention","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that a sticking point was Pyongyang 's demand for total sanctions relief .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Foreign Minister Ri Yong-ho said","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"the nation had only asked for partial sanctions relief in exchange for disabling its main nuclear complex at Yongbyon and permanently halting nuclear and long-range rocket testing .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"`` This proposal was the biggest denuclearisation measure","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"we could take at the present stage","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"when taking into consideration the current level of confidence between the DPRK","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"[ North Korea ]","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"and the United States , ''","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"said Mr Ri .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"North Korea 's state-run media struck an upbeat tone on Friday ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"without mentioning","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"that the summit had ended early .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"News agency KCNA said","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"the two leaders had promised to remain in touch","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"in order to continue the `` epochal development '' of bilateral relations and the denuclearisation of the Korean peninsula .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"`` The top leaders of the two countries highly appreciated at the one-on-one talks and extended talks","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"that a remarkable progress has been made in the historic course","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"of implementing the Singapore joint statement , ''","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"said KCNA .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"On Friday , Mr Trump tweeted :","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"`` I never like being misinterpreted ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"but especially when it comes to Otto Warmbier and his great family . ''","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"that Warmbier and his family `` have become a tremendous symbol of strong passion and strength ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"which will last for many years into the future '' .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"`` I love Otto","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"and think of him often ! ''","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"It comes","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"after Democrats led criticism of the president ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"pointing out","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"that Mr Trump has previously sided with strongmen .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"After meeting Russian President Vladimir Putin in Helsinki in July 2018 ,","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"the US president said","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"he believed his denial","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"that the Kremlin sought to interfere in the 2016 US election ,","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"despite US intelligence officials concluding otherwise .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"Critics also pointed out","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that last December , Mr Trump defended Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"despite CIA officials ' belief","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"that the royal had ordered the gruesome murder of a US-based reporter , Jamal Khashoggi .","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"Later on Friday , White House aide Kellyanne Conway said","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"Mr Trump `` agrees with the Warmbier family","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"and holds North Korea responsible '' for their son 's death .","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"`` He has deep affection","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"and shares the grief with the Warmbier family , ''","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"she told Fox News .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"`` What the president is saying is that there 's no indication","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"Chairman Kim knew","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"what happened to Otto Warmbier","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"when it happened , ''","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"she added .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"Russian state-controlled media","depth":4},{"id":129,"text":"- once quite the fans of Donald Trump -","depth":4},{"id":130,"text":"were scathing about the US president 's performance at the talks .","depth":3},{"id":131,"text":"A Channel One report from the summit said","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"it had `` failed miserably ,","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"dealing another blow to the reputation of the American leader '' .","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"Over on Rossiya 1 TV , a presenter said","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"the outcome was `` predictable '' ,","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"as Mr Trump had `` arrived at the new summit with old tactics '' ,","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"while NTV pointed out","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"that Russia had warned","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"Washington 's `` position of ultimatums '' would not work .","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"One Rossiya 1 presenter suggested","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"Mr Trump had only been interested in distracting people from the testimony of his former lawyer , Michael Cohen .","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"In the papers , the independent Novaya Gazeta looks on the bright side ,","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"that the leaders","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"- while `` still extremely far from the Nobel Peace Prize '' -","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"have at least stopped swapping insults .","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"But in mass tabloid Moskovsky Komsomolets , one pundit is withering ,","depth":5},{"id":148,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":149,"text":"one `` has to understand the core of a subject","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"to make compromises ,","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"while Trump is the most ignorant head of state in US history '' .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":303,"left":279,"right":302,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":279,"left":175,"right":278,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":168,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":164,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":163,"right":12,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":155,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":154,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":154,"left":0,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":157,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":4,"right":156,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":161,"left":159,"right":160,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":7,"rig